    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like puzzles? Do you like dice? Do you like <i>really difficult</i> 3D puzzles that you solve by rolling dice around?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras/17d4b6fb49dea3776e0f0cde8179a330.avif?t=1759427537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras_big/17d4b6fb49dea3776e0f0cde8179a330.avif?t=1759427537 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Your Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of each puzzle is simple: reach the exit with a die. See: it's just over there! Sometimes it will be <i>right next to you.</i> How hard can it be?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turns out it can be very, very hard indeed. Which is why there's an 'undo' button and no time limit. I mean, the sun will burn out at some point but until then, no pressure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras/586c96216397c08cc96ace8310796e11.avif?t=1759427537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras_big/586c96216397c08cc96ace8310796e11.avif?t=1759427537 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Non-Linear and Endlessly Innovative</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll uncover hundreds of puzzles, dozens of cunning puzzle mechanics, and a whole interconnected map to explore. Collect dice and use them to solve old puzzles new ways, find coins and buy upgrades to help you track down secrets, and become the undisputed Dice King! It's totally worth the effort! And the money! Especially the money. So worth it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras/f21c67e8302632608ce3793929941a46.avif?t=1759427537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045970/extras_big/f21c67e8302632608ce3793929941a46.avif?t=1759427537 width=800 height=224 /></span></p>",
